    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it wasnt just a pattern though.. it was like the exact same coffee stain on the upholstery. i'm telling you it wasnt just my brain playing tricks. it felt like the world actually stuttered for a second. like a frame dropped in a video. do you think there's any actual scientific reason why someone would see something like that? like, is there a theory for when reality doesn't look right?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
